<h2>Licensing Enquiries</h2>

<p><em>Sound On Sound</em> has a long tradition of licensing our articles to other publishers around the world. If you wish to talk to us about individual articles or any aspect of the magazine / web site content,&nbsp;please email Dave Lockwood, Editorial Director via our <a href="/contact">Contact SOS</a> form.</p>

<h2>Repurposing SOS Content</h2>

<p>Please visit our <strong><a href="https://www.soundonsound.com/information/guidelines-repurposing-sound-sound-content" target="_blank">Guidelines</a></strong> page to find out what is permitted.</p>

