          <a href="/magazine/2024-05"><img src=data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw== class="b-lazy" loading="lazy" data-src="https://dt7v1i9vyp3mf.cloudfront.net/styles/cover_large/s3/covers/2405ukl-isyoDNEOuMSl4pH2HLPSnU4wODNAeY9u.jpg" width="140" height="198" alt="SOS (UK Edition) May 2024" title="SOS (UK Edition) May 2024" />  

  

